# Nightly logical backup, same cadence as the systemd timer it replaces
# (deploy/systemd/pi-audit-backup.timer: 02:30 UTC daily).
# Output redirected to /proc/1/fd/{1,2} so cron job output shows up in `docker logs
# <container>` — PID 1 in this container is crond itself (entrypoint.sh execs `crond -f`).
30 2 * * * /scripts/backup-once.sh >>/proc/1/fd/1 2>>/proc/1/fd/2
